The paper deals with a multi-agent framework for distributed optimization, which is a topic that falls under machine learning and optimization. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also involves distributed computing, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also deals with control systems, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper involves multi-agent networks, which could fall under cs.MA (Multiagent Systems).
